  "keyFeatures": [
    "Flexible task definitions for navigation, rearrangement, instruction following, and question answering",
    "Support for diverse embodied agents including commercial robots (Spot, Fetch) and humanoids",
    "RL and IL training algorithms including PPO, DD-PPO, HRL, and imitation learning",
    "Multi-agent simulation with human-robot interaction in Habitat 3.0",
    "Human-in-the-loop (HITL) framework for interactive data collection and evaluation",
    "Gym-compatible interface for standard RL training pipelines",
    "Hydra-based hierarchical configuration system",
    "VectorEnv and ThreadedVectorEnv for parallelized environment rollouts"
  ],
